    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台恶意铺品细则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1308425579423612928",
    "content": "<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 32px; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">您好，为适应业务发展，针对</span></span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; text-decoration-line: underline; color: blue; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1303597708439298048\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">《京东开放平台恶意铺品细则</span>》</a></span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">进行调整<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; background-color: white;\">，现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年11月28日- 2025年12月4日，规则预计于2025年12月5日生效，公示期满后平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">核心调整点：</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">1、修改处理措施，处理措施中增加&ldquo;全店商品下架和扣除店铺资金（包括保证金、货款等）&rdquo;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">修订后处理措施如下：</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东有权根据违规情节严重程度，对涉事商家店铺及关联店铺采取预警、开具违约单、管控、限权、关店等处理措施。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">管控措施</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">包括但不限于：违规商品下架且限制重新上架、限制店铺内商品发布数量上限、限制每日新发商品数、<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">全店商品下架</span>、全店商品流量降权 / 屏蔽、限制提报平台营销活动、加收风险保证金、<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">扣除店铺资金（包括保证金、货款等）</span>、限制关联品类商品上架；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">限权措施</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">包括但不限于：限制新品标识申请、限制厂自模式使用权限、限制 ISV 工具部分功能使用、限制商品信息批量编辑权限。</span></p>",
